snippet.title: Mechanic Heroes - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Build your team of mechanics and work together to repair and deliver as many cars as possible before the time runs out!
Earn money and continue your adventure to the next challenge.
Playable with up to 4 players, locally or online, Mechanic Heroes will make you love mechanics or simply hate your friends.

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2061620/Mechanic_Heroes/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/MechanicHeroes
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/lategamestudios
Website: https://www.lategamestudios.com/#mh 
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/lategamestudios/
